    <h2>The upper channel is vanishing</h2>
    <div class="lsl-prose">
      <p>The tactical edge <em>per opportunity</em> stays large &mdash; up high, laddering still won big. But the opportunities to be up high are collapsing cycle over cycle. Maximum channel position reached, by four-year window:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lsl-table-wrap">
      <table class="lsl-table">
