    </div>
    <div class="lsl-prose">
      <p>As Bitcoin matures it increasingly lives low-to-mid channel, where decisiveness won &mdash; consistent with the volatility compression on <a href="/the-doubling-ladder">The Doubling Ladder</a> and the Power Law&rsquo;s shrinking cycle peaks. The clever &ldquo;wait for the top to pass, then ladder down&rdquo; move is one you rarely get to use anymore. The channel mostly just says <em>commit</em>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

